I hope you don't mind, KSL. But I'm getting suck of these battles and I'm 
going to pick on your characters for now. Feel free to pick back.


* Iron Raptor backed up and away from Prowl, thinking of how the battle was 
going on and that she wasn't going to waste her time with him at the moment. 
He could look after himself.
But she was going to talk to Iris to see if she could get his SBM disabled, 
since he didn't need to use it when he couldn't controle it.
He almost killed her the last time and was almost close to doing it now so 
something had to be done.

Turning around and away from Prowl Iron spotted Demon Wulf fire at the CF, 
growling and storming at him.*

" Leave my ship alone you fur covered tick!"

* She covered ground quickly.
Across the field Iris spotted IR turn away from Prowl, narrowinf her eyes 
and looking at him while the commander delt with the enemy.
She didn't trust a wild beast loose on the field, aiming her weapon at him. 
She had to put him to an end, knocking him out so that at least there was 
one left who could controle hers.
Iris fired, directly at his head.
< It's for your own good.> she thought to herself.*
